REM
REM     EAMIRWR1 J86      WRITE AN ITEM RECORD
REM     EAMIRWR2 J86      WRITE AN ITEM RECORD NO AUTOUNLOCK
REM     EAMIRRD1 J86      READ AN ITEM RECORD
